API.ADK

Class FilterList

  • java.lang.Object
    • API.ADK.FilterList

  • public class FilterList
extends java.lang.Object
    Structure for the Filter list. It can be standard or extended filter list. This class is used internally for software filtering and externally for reading the Filter list.

    hroesdiyono
